                     <interp inst="t18220703-97-person847" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am the mother of the child, whose name is Eleanor - we live at Bagnigge-wells. I sent her out to Exmouth-street, to buy some tape - she had a necklace on then. My husband's name is 
               <persName id="t18220703-97-person848">
                  George 
                  Francis
               <interp inst="t18220703-97-person848" type="surname" value="Francis"></interp>
